WEBVTT

01:40.420 --> 01:45.930
[Speed and Love]

01:46.250 --> 01:48.810
[Episode 23]

02:16.230 --> 02:19.190
[Friend request: I'm Mu]

03:18.100 --> 03:18.850
Moon?

03:20.240 --> 03:21.000
Mu?

03:23.350 --> 03:24.240
The moon?

03:25.680 --> 03:26.810
What a coincidence.

03:27.070 --> 03:28.070
Who could that be?

03:29.240 --> 03:31.500
They actually made your dream come true.

03:47.240 --> 03:48.900
Why did you choose this major?

03:52.430 --> 03:53.760
Ever since I was little,

03:53.960 --> 03:56.290
I never had any grand ambitions or dreams.

03:56.720 --> 03:58.070
My only dream

03:58.510 --> 03:59.440
was you.

04:00.430 --> 04:01.870
You gave up this path,

04:02.680 --> 04:04.160
but I had to walk it for you.

04:16.190 --> 04:17.680
I chose his path,

04:18.600 --> 04:20.600
and he fulfilled my dream.

04:42.060 --> 04:44.060
[Sleep early]

06:02.680 --> 06:03.810
How are you feeling?

06:08.510 --> 06:10.570
I still can't engage my core muscles.

06:11.040 --> 06:12.240
You can't handle

06:12.270 --> 06:13.930
this much exercise right now.

06:14.000 --> 06:15.000
Be patient.

06:16.000 --> 06:17.510
How much longer will it take?

06:17.510 --> 06:19.510
You've persevered all these years.

06:19.750 --> 06:20.810
Haste makes waste.

06:22.150 --> 06:22.910
Okay.

06:48.100 --> 06:50.150
[Got it]

06:52.190 --> 06:53.120
All these years,

06:53.240 --> 06:55.600
I've been thinking about you
day and night.

06:55.600 --> 06:57.659
Yet you're so indifferent toward me.

07:03.680 --> 07:05.480
I need to do something to shake you up

07:05.480 --> 07:07.340
and see if you can really stay put.

07:16.270 --> 07:17.000
Jiang Mu.

07:17.480 --> 07:19.410
Xining's wedding is next Tuesday.

07:19.440 --> 07:20.360
You must come.

07:20.750 --> 07:22.010
We're like her family.

07:23.010 --> 07:24.680
Besides, you're the only single girl

07:24.680 --> 07:25.710
in our institute.

07:26.200 --> 07:27.680
Come and try to catch the bouquet

07:27.680 --> 07:28.510
for good luck.

07:31.460 --> 07:32.550
Okay, got it.

07:33.070 --> 07:35.270
Alright, I'll send you the invitation.

07:46.010 --> 07:50.550
[Xining's wedding is next Tuesday.
Don't forget to go.]

08:23.450 --> 08:28.050
[Wedding Invitation]

08:54.750 --> 08:56.270
I'm getting married next Tuesday.

08:56.270 --> 08:57.120
You promised

08:57.320 --> 08:58.790
you'd come to my wedding.

09:25.960 --> 09:27.270
It will be in Nanjing.

09:27.550 --> 09:28.750
My family's not here.

09:29.000 --> 09:31.000
I only have you, my brother, around.

09:31.050 --> 09:33.080
Although we're not related by blood,

09:33.080 --> 09:35.080
we're still kinda family.

09:35.430 --> 09:37.240
You must come to support me.

09:37.390 --> 09:39.520
I can't let his side think
I have no family of my own,

09:39.520 --> 09:41.380
or they'll bully me in the future.

09:49.220 --> 09:50.480
The wedding customs here

09:50.480 --> 09:51.960
require the bride's family to prepare

09:51.960 --> 09:53.200
gold jewelry sets.

10:01.050 --> 10:02.120
You want these?

10:05.550 --> 10:07.750
Of course, I can't be outdone by others.

10:10.640 --> 10:11.480
See you at the wedding.

10:11.480 --> 10:12.290
Don't be late.

10:12.750 --> 10:13.340
Oh, right.

10:13.340 --> 10:16.070
Don't forget to prepare
a fat red envelope for me.

10:19.710 --> 10:21.950
Keep acting all cold and distant.

10:22.560 --> 10:24.560
Let's see how long you can keep it up.

12:18.630 --> 12:20.410
[How do you feel now?]

12:24.200 --> 12:25.630
[Mu]

12:35.550 --> 12:37.150
So are you more unhappy

12:37.150 --> 12:38.720
or more happy about it?

12:42.960 --> 12:45.220
I've prepared all the gold jewelry sets.

12:46.440 --> 12:48.240
And I've got the cash gift ready.

12:48.800 --> 12:49.930
Do you still want it?

12:50.440 --> 12:52.080
Yes, of course I do.

12:52.550 --> 12:54.320
I won't be polite with you.

12:55.510 --> 12:56.970
How should I give it to you?

12:58.910 --> 13:00.000
Well,

13:00.630 --> 13:01.690
in a couple of days.

13:02.750 --> 13:05.280
I need to go to Beijing
on a business trip soon.

13:09.000 --> 13:11.320
I really am getting married.

13:11.900 --> 13:13.080
It's just that
I had a fight with my boyfriend

13:13.080 --> 13:14.480
a few days ago

13:14.790 --> 13:15.480
and, in a fit of anger,

13:15.480 --> 13:17.200
said we'd put the wedding on hold for now.

13:17.200 --> 13:18.320
Just temporarily.

13:19.600 --> 13:20.840
Maybe in a couple of days,

13:20.840 --> 13:21.720
if he sweet-talks me,

13:21.720 --> 13:22.720
I'll feel better

13:22.830 --> 13:24.560
and agree to get married again.

13:30.080 --> 13:31.000
Don't you think

13:31.360 --> 13:33.960
I'm really bad at relationships?

13:34.240 --> 13:36.390
I get sweet-talked by men so easily.

13:36.670 --> 13:38.800
If this keeps up, I'm bound to lose out.

13:39.120 --> 13:40.390
You must back me up.

13:40.510 --> 13:42.510
Don't let me get taken advantage of.

13:43.720 --> 13:44.430
Okay.

14:03.610 --> 14:04.410
Everyone,

14:04.430 --> 14:05.820
today we're focusing on

14:05.840 --> 14:07.490
exoplanetary stellar systems.

14:07.490 --> 14:09.200
By combining
high-precision spectroscopic observations

14:09.200 --> 14:10.710
with celestial mechanics simulations,

14:10.710 --> 14:11.950
we analyze the energy dissipation pathways

14:11.950 --> 14:13.840
triggered by tidal torques

14:13.910 --> 14:15.720
and quantify how interactions

14:15.750 --> 14:17.360
with circumstellar disks
affect dissipation efficiency.

14:17.360 --> 14:19.480
Our study reveals the coupled evolution
of orbital eccentricity

14:19.480 --> 14:21.240
and tidal dissipation,

14:21.430 --> 14:22.880
providing key theoretical support

14:22.880 --> 14:26.120
for accurately predicting the long-term stability of astronomical systems.

14:26.120 --> 14:28.270
Alright. Is everything clear to everyone?

14:28.270 --> 14:29.800
That concludes today's meeting.

14:29.800 --> 14:30.460
Dismissed.

14:48.670 --> 14:50.320
If I don't text you first,

14:50.460 --> 14:52.990
will you never take the initiative
to text me?

15:00.510 --> 15:01.510
I'll be back today.

15:01.510 --> 15:03.770
I brought you some Beijing specialties.

15:06.450 --> 15:07.510
I'm not in Nanjing.

15:13.080 --> 15:15.000
To simplify the vehicle structure,

15:15.000 --> 15:15.910
we'll remove

15:16.030 --> 15:18.360
the rear-seat module in the new model.

15:19.900 --> 15:21.080
The overall body structure

15:21.080 --> 15:23.430
will be limited to within 150 parts,

15:25.670 --> 15:28.600
and the vehicle
will retain only 3 physical switches

15:29.110 --> 15:30.960
to control the windows, doors,

15:31.030 --> 15:32.750
and ceiling light.

15:33.030 --> 15:34.600
Next, please turn to page 3.

15:37.150 --> 15:38.600
On page 3...

16:16.750 --> 16:18.150
Not replying to me again?

16:23.080 --> 16:25.200
Hello, I'd like a chocolate cake.

16:25.790 --> 16:27.650
Certainly. Please wait a moment.

16:31.550 --> 16:33.160
Ms. Jiang? Long time no see.

16:33.360 --> 16:34.920
Have you been away on a business trip?

16:34.920 --> 16:35.780
I just got back.

16:36.160 --> 16:38.030
I brought some treats for your boss.

16:38.030 --> 16:40.030
He's not here.
You can share them among yourselves.

16:40.030 --> 16:41.270
What are these?

16:41.670 --> 16:43.030
Some Beijing specialties.

16:43.030 --> 16:43.960
They taste quite good.

16:43.960 --> 16:45.290
-Thank you.
-Thank you.

16:45.840 --> 16:47.300
A "Moon" for you, as usual?

16:48.430 --> 16:50.200
No need. Our boss instructed us

16:50.320 --> 16:52.180
that your orders are on the house.

16:52.910 --> 16:55.080
Please have a seat. I'll make your coffee.

16:55.080 --> 16:55.790
Thanks.

16:57.510 --> 16:58.600
Lightning.

17:01.270 --> 17:02.150
Ms. Jiang,

17:02.350 --> 17:04.190
you're friends with our boss, right?

17:04.190 --> 17:05.839
No wonder Quiet knows you.

17:06.359 --> 17:08.430
Of course. It's my dog.

17:12.950 --> 17:13.599
Xiao Jia,

17:14.150 --> 17:15.480
can I ask you something?

17:16.190 --> 17:18.119
Is your boss married?

17:18.470 --> 17:20.359
He is usually very busy.

17:20.599 --> 17:21.910
I really don't know much

17:21.910 --> 17:23.430
about his personal life.

17:23.910 --> 17:26.109
Then why is he always on business trips?

17:26.150 --> 17:27.390
Is it because of work,

17:27.520 --> 17:28.910
or does he work in another city?

17:28.910 --> 17:31.040
The boss doesn't work for any company.

17:31.040 --> 17:32.150
With his health,

17:32.190 --> 17:34.190
he can't handle a nine-to-five job.

17:34.390 --> 17:36.050
What's wrong with his health?

17:38.760 --> 17:39.630
Well...

17:40.230 --> 17:42.150
He has to run the coffee shop

17:42.520 --> 17:43.850
and also attend school.

17:43.990 --> 17:45.600
If he took on a full-time job
on top of that,

17:45.600 --> 17:47.930
even a healthy person couldn't handle it.

17:53.160 --> 17:53.890
Your coffee.

17:54.520 --> 17:55.080
Enjoy.

17:55.390 --> 17:57.790
-Thank you.
-Ms. Jiang, I'll be going then.

18:22.710 --> 18:24.390
Thanks for the free coffee.

18:32.560 --> 18:33.820
I'll be back tomorrow.

18:49.300 --> 18:50.410
Ms. Jiang, you...

18:51.280 --> 18:53.810
Tell your boss to come to my place
to pick it up.

18:55.570 --> 18:57.290
Hurry, call Boss.

19:02.990 --> 19:03.560
Boss,

19:03.840 --> 19:05.840
Quiet was taken away by Ms. Jiang.

19:09.230 --> 19:09.910
Okay.

19:11.760 --> 19:12.710
What did he say?

19:13.150 --> 19:14.150
He just said

19:14.380 --> 19:15.510
he got it.

19:16.800 --> 19:17.780
Got it?

19:23.150 --> 19:24.360
Lightning.

19:25.390 --> 19:27.390
Baby Lightning, did you sleep well?

19:27.710 --> 19:29.320
Good boy. Look at me.

19:29.670 --> 19:30.840
Here, here.

19:31.240 --> 19:31.910
Did you sleep well?

19:31.910 --> 19:33.440
Tell me, did you sleep well?

19:35.230 --> 19:36.120
Give me a hug.

19:36.280 --> 19:37.390
Give me a hug.

19:38.840 --> 19:41.100
Alright. Mommy will take you out to play.

19:43.360 --> 19:44.520
Let's go.

19:44.950 --> 19:45.670
Come on!

20:21.520 --> 20:24.050
At least he has Lightning
to keep him company.

20:24.280 --> 20:25.760
I have nothing.

20:37.490 --> 20:38.690
Send me your address.

20:40.630 --> 20:41.880
Building 6, Unit 4,

20:41.990 --> 20:43.800
Apartment 302, Jingyuancheng.

20:47.500 --> 20:49.030
I'll be there in 30 minutes.

21:19.360 --> 21:20.320
It's strange.

21:21.120 --> 21:22.080
Over the years,

21:22.760 --> 21:24.120
I've met so many people—

21:25.080 --> 21:26.040
handsome ones,

21:26.600 --> 21:27.670
wealthy ones,

21:28.280 --> 21:29.560
highly educated ones—

21:30.560 --> 21:33.090
yet none of them
ever made my heart race again.

21:34.360 --> 21:35.280
Sometimes

21:36.080 --> 21:37.670
I even wonder if I've lost

21:37.670 --> 21:39.400
the ability to feel that spark.

21:40.300 --> 21:41.170
However,

21:41.850 --> 21:43.450
after seeing Jin Zhao again,

21:44.190 --> 21:46.280
the uncontrollable nervousness
and excitement

21:46.280 --> 21:47.340
made me realize...

21:48.910 --> 21:49.800
that maybe

21:50.650 --> 21:52.500
only this man before me

21:53.580 --> 21:56.030
can easily stir my heart.

21:59.800 --> 22:00.950
Have you had dinner?

22:02.080 --> 22:03.190
I ate on my way back.

22:04.600 --> 22:05.880
Didn't I give you the apartment number?

22:05.880 --> 22:07.140
Why didn't you come up?

22:11.390 --> 22:12.280
He's not home.

22:16.910 --> 22:18.640
You're living at his place now?

22:19.760 --> 22:20.960
We don't own this place.

22:20.960 --> 22:22.360
We rent it together.

22:23.120 --> 22:24.600
Aren't you getting married?

22:24.600 --> 22:26.530
You're not planning to buy a house?

22:27.220 --> 22:28.300
We can't afford it.

22:28.370 --> 22:30.350
He earns just over 4000 a month.

22:30.390 --> 22:32.950
After insurance and provident fund,
there's not much left.

22:32.950 --> 22:34.390
I'm just an intern.

22:34.760 --> 22:37.230
I was thinking that once I go full-time,

22:37.430 --> 22:39.290
I could save a bit more to help him.

22:39.520 --> 22:41.280
Besides, the wedding was called off,

22:41.280 --> 22:43.480
so buying a house isn't urgent anymore.

22:43.560 --> 22:45.760
I thought I'd just find a place to get by.

22:46.760 --> 22:48.960
How dare you mention the wedding again?

22:49.660 --> 22:50.860
How dare you lie?

22:51.230 --> 22:52.760
And how dare you believe it?

22:56.490 --> 22:58.950
Where are my gold jewelry sets
and cash gift?

22:59.620 --> 23:00.680
They're in the car.

23:01.360 --> 23:02.760
Want me to bring them now?

23:03.560 --> 23:05.360
No rush. Just keep them with you.

23:05.670 --> 23:07.400
It's not like they'll run away.

23:11.630 --> 23:12.960
I just finished dinner.

23:12.990 --> 23:14.720
I'll take a walk and see you off.

23:25.040 --> 23:27.120
Didn't Sanlai say Lightning was lost?

23:27.120 --> 23:28.520
How did it end up with you?

23:31.910 --> 23:33.710
You just got back and settled in.

23:33.950 --> 23:35.230
Maybe he didn't want to trouble you,

23:35.230 --> 23:36.360
so he left it with me.

23:37.230 --> 23:38.760
You don't mind the trouble?

23:39.950 --> 23:40.710
It's fine.

23:43.360 --> 23:46.020
Who was it
that wouldn't let me keep a dog before?

23:49.840 --> 23:51.150
You've really got a big heart.

23:51.150 --> 23:52.470
You're keeping your ex-girlfriend's dog,

23:52.470 --> 23:53.600
running a coffee shop

23:53.600 --> 23:54.910
named after her,

23:55.280 --> 23:57.740
and now you're even
walking the dog with her.

23:57.810 --> 23:59.140
Doesn't your wife mind?

24:00.850 --> 24:01.530
What?

24:01.980 --> 24:03.170
Am I not your ex?

24:06.040 --> 24:07.700
Doesn't your boyfriend mind?

24:08.560 --> 24:11.510
You're out taking a walk
with another man late at night.

24:11.510 --> 24:13.380
Of course he doesn't mind.

24:13.730 --> 24:17.130
He even goes out singing
with other pretty girls all the time.

24:23.700 --> 24:25.160
Then how does he treat you?

24:26.390 --> 24:27.360
Just so-so.

24:27.910 --> 24:30.000
Just last week we had a big fight

24:30.030 --> 24:31.140
over a phone.

24:34.630 --> 24:36.630
I've been using my phone for over 2 years,

24:36.630 --> 24:38.090
so I wanted to get a new one.

24:38.230 --> 24:40.290
He said I don't play games on my phone,

24:40.520 --> 24:41.520
so I don't need a good one,

24:41.520 --> 24:43.520
and that I just use it to chat anyway.

24:43.520 --> 24:45.040
So he spent all that money

24:45.040 --> 24:46.470
on gaming gear instead.

24:47.340 --> 24:49.270
Then what do you see in him exactly?

24:57.120 --> 24:58.000
I'm getting older,

24:58.000 --> 25:00.130
so I just settled for someone to get by.

25:27.090 --> 25:29.020
Don't joke like this with me again.

25:35.120 --> 25:35.910
Go back now.

25:36.390 --> 25:37.150
I'm leaving.

25:44.420 --> 25:46.030
Why do you say I'm joking?

25:46.910 --> 25:48.510
Why can't I say these things?

25:59.190 --> 26:00.360
It hurts to hear.

26:17.270 --> 26:18.470
Good, it should hurt.

26:18.630 --> 26:19.760
Do you think these 6 years,

26:19.760 --> 26:20.840
yearning day and night for you,

26:20.840 --> 26:22.150
have been easy for me?

27:00.710 --> 27:02.570
Why did you take my dog away again?

27:40.740 --> 27:42.920
♪ What would I do? ♪

27:42.940 --> 27:45.420
♪ If I have 45 minutes? ♪

27:44.140 --> 27:46.900
[Meteorological Bureau]

27:45.970 --> 27:48.670
♪ Would I write a song? ♪

27:49.160 --> 27:51.310
♪ No, I don't think so ♪

27:52.870 --> 27:55.140
♪ What would I do? ♪

27:55.200 --> 27:57.560
♪ If I have 70 seconds? ♪

27:57.830 --> 28:00.560
♪ Would I get a drink or two? ♪

28:01.100 --> 28:03.570
♪ No, I don't think so ♪

28:04.390 --> 28:07.580
♪ I'd rather get on that bus ♪

28:08.100 --> 28:10.800
♪ Find you where you are ♪

28:11.270 --> 28:13.520
♪ To talk about the cloud ♪

28:13.710 --> 28:16.370
♪ That looks just like a kangaroo ♪

28:17.140 --> 28:20.120
♪ And the old man on the street ♪

28:19.320 --> 28:20.450
It's going to rain tomorrow
and the temperature will drop.

28:20.450 --> 28:23.290
♪ Sat there with his dog ♪

28:20.950 --> 28:22.350
Remember to dress warmly

28:22.390 --> 28:23.650
and bring an umbrella.

28:23.700 --> 28:26.000
♪ Asking you if you're willing ♪

28:26.020 --> 28:28.490
♪ To accompany me too ♪

28:35.010 --> 28:37.240
♪ Would you like that? ♪

28:37.910 --> 28:40.820
♪ Would you like that? ♪

29:04.620 --> 29:11.900
[The Moon Represents My Heart]

29:20.830 --> 29:26.850
♪ You ask me how deep I love you ♪

29:27.240 --> 29:31.830
♪ How much I love you ♪

29:32.700 --> 29:35.880
♪ My love is real ♪

29:35.910 --> 29:38.840
♪ My love is sincere ♪

29:39.000 --> 29:44.650
♪ The moon represents my heart ♪

29:45.760 --> 29:51.620
♪ You ask me how deep I love you ♪

29:51.920 --> 29:56.590
♪ How much I love you ♪

29:57.620 --> 30:00.830
♪ My love will never change ♪

30:00.860 --> 30:03.730
♪ My love will stay the same ♪

30:03.900 --> 30:09.080
♪ The moon represents my heart ♪

30:08.090 --> 30:09.020
Please sit down.

30:09.950 --> 30:15.500
♪ A gentle kiss ♪

30:10.710 --> 30:13.150
That's a very good question.

30:13.770 --> 30:15.190
We've also made optimizations

30:15.190 --> 30:16.360
in active suspension technology.

30:16.200 --> 30:21.950
♪ Has touched my heart ♪

30:16.880 --> 30:18.230
We plan to equip each wheel

30:18.230 --> 30:19.190
with a power unit

30:19.280 --> 30:21.520
and a dual-valve continuous
damping control system.

30:21.520 --> 30:23.470
Combined with road preview data

30:22.260 --> 30:28.150
♪ A deep love ♪

30:23.800 --> 30:26.080
and cloud-based data,

30:26.150 --> 30:28.390
this can reduce the driver's burden.

30:28.580 --> 30:34.760
♪ Has me miss you till now♪

30:29.990 --> 30:30.590
Everyone,

30:30.950 --> 30:32.840
innovation in automobiles
has no finish line,

30:32.840 --> 30:34.670
but a human-centered approach
will always be our direction.

30:34.670 --> 30:35.880
I hope everyone can maintain

30:35.390 --> 30:41.070
♪ You ask me how deep I love you ♪

30:35.880 --> 30:37.540
a deep respect for user needs,

30:37.600 --> 30:39.190
so we can develop

30:39.430 --> 30:40.630
better Chinese cars.

30:41.200 --> 30:46.050
♪ How much I love you ♪

30:47.000 --> 30:50.150
♪ Go think about it ♪

30:50.200 --> 30:53.220
♪ Go take a look ♪

30:53.240 --> 30:58.950
♪ The moon represents my heart ♪

31:59.600 --> 32:01.150
Ms. Jiang, you're here.

32:01.560 --> 32:02.420
Please come in.

32:02.800 --> 32:03.760
Where's your boss?

32:03.760 --> 32:04.950
He's not here.

32:05.430 --> 32:07.430
Have you been busy with work lately?

32:07.470 --> 32:08.280
Pretty busy.

32:12.670 --> 32:14.710
Xiao Jia, I'll get straight to the point.

32:14.710 --> 32:16.360
Has your boss met all the girls

32:16.360 --> 32:17.760
listed in that register?

32:17.760 --> 32:18.910
Of course not.

32:20.390 --> 32:21.990
Our boss is already married.

32:22.120 --> 32:23.780
His wife and child are abroad.

32:24.560 --> 32:25.430
Married?

32:26.200 --> 32:27.320
Are you sure?

32:27.560 --> 32:28.390
I'm sure.

32:28.600 --> 32:30.360
He told us himself.

32:31.570 --> 32:33.260
W-well...

32:33.750 --> 32:35.000
Have you met

32:35.210 --> 32:35.990
his wife and child?

32:35.990 --> 32:36.840
No.

32:36.870 --> 32:38.470
We haven't even seen a photo.

32:38.530 --> 32:40.260
He keeps them very well hidden.

32:41.310 --> 32:42.630
Not even a photo?

32:43.230 --> 32:45.210
Maybe he made it up

32:45.230 --> 32:46.120
and was lying to you.

32:46.120 --> 32:47.630
If he didn't have a wife and child,

32:47.630 --> 32:50.390
what's the point
of making up a family to deceive us?

32:50.390 --> 32:51.650
To keep admirers away.

32:52.060 --> 32:52.880
Well,

32:52.900 --> 32:54.510
that does make some sense.

32:55.470 --> 32:56.980
Jin Zhao is pretty much a jerk.

32:56.980 --> 32:57.910
He hates trouble

32:58.120 --> 32:59.580
and often talks nonsense.

32:59.800 --> 33:02.400
He just doesn't want women
making a move on him.

33:03.470 --> 33:04.630
I just remembered something.

33:04.630 --> 33:06.630
Last time I went to his place
to deliver something,

33:06.630 --> 33:08.360
I saw a woman there.

33:08.950 --> 33:09.710
A woman?

33:10.320 --> 33:11.380
What kind of woman?

33:11.520 --> 33:13.120
Just a very beautiful woman.

33:13.470 --> 33:15.000
How beautiful?

33:15.390 --> 33:16.230
The kind that

33:16.390 --> 33:18.880
has the elegant air of a boss's wife.

33:20.390 --> 33:22.150
Now that you mentioned it, I remember too.

33:22.150 --> 33:24.360
Last time I called his home

33:24.470 --> 33:25.520
to ask about Quiet,

33:25.520 --> 33:27.040
a woman answered.

33:27.630 --> 33:29.190
She also sounded very...

33:29.190 --> 33:29.910
Enough!

33:31.390 --> 33:32.080
Xiao Jia,

33:32.230 --> 33:34.360
give me your boss's address right now.

33:43.190 --> 33:45.120
I'd like to see what she looks like.

34:25.730 --> 34:27.330
You're looking for Jin Zhao?

34:39.020 --> 34:40.620
She even knows the password?

34:41.679 --> 34:43.030
Come in and wait inside.

35:05.870 --> 35:07.270
These are your slippers?

35:08.140 --> 35:08.820
Yes.

35:10.710 --> 35:13.710
I think we only have this one pair
of women's slippers.

35:15.160 --> 35:16.960
Why don't you wear these for now?

35:17.130 --> 35:18.360
All guests wear them.

35:18.870 --> 35:20.530
Try them on and see if they fit.

35:21.880 --> 35:22.840
Thank you.

35:31.450 --> 35:33.110
Guest? You're a guest.

35:33.200 --> 35:34.800
Your whole family is guests.

35:35.680 --> 35:36.810
Please, have a seat.

35:37.870 --> 35:39.470
What would you like to drink?

35:40.470 --> 35:41.470
Anything is fine.

35:42.430 --> 35:44.630
"Anything" is the hardest to deal with.

35:44.640 --> 35:45.430
How about coffee?

35:45.430 --> 35:47.690
I brought these beans back from Vietnam.

35:48.770 --> 35:50.300
No need to go to the trouble.

35:50.730 --> 35:52.400
Alright, then just water.

35:59.570 --> 36:00.430
How about this?

36:00.460 --> 36:02.390
Sit for a bit. I'll go take a shower.

36:03.110 --> 36:05.110
You're taking a shower at his place?

36:06.380 --> 36:07.310
Yes. I live here.

36:08.160 --> 36:09.570
-You…
-Come on. I stink.

36:09.590 --> 36:10.390
I can't stand it anymore.

36:10.390 --> 36:12.200
A bunch of men
were smoking around me tonight.

36:12.200 --> 36:15.660
I really can't stand the smell of smoke.
Make yourself at home.

36:19.840 --> 36:23.560
[Epilogue]

36:23.670 --> 36:26.820
♪ Waiting, still waiting ♪

36:27.130 --> 36:30.070
♪ You, weaving through my heart ♪

36:30.540 --> 36:34.330
♪ My thoughts of you will never cease ♪

36:34.350 --> 36:39.040
♪ Waiting for your ship to arrive ♪

36:39.150 --> 36:41.830
♪ Waiting, still waiting ♪

36:42.220 --> 36:45.670
♪ You, chasing after the moon ♪

36:46.230 --> 36:48.500
♪ Scattered across the sky ♪

36:48.580 --> 36:52.260
♪ And me, here by your side ♪

37:10.290 --> 37:13.190
♪ Stars are twinkling in the sky ♪

37:11.550 --> 37:12.800
So beautiful!

37:13.580 --> 37:16.550
♪ Like your twinkling eyes ♪

37:16.800 --> 37:19.570
♪ Telling me ♪

37:18.320 --> 37:18.950
Zhao.

37:20.860 --> 37:23.440
♪ A beautiful dream from afar ♪

37:21.950 --> 37:23.720
No matter what you're planning to do,

37:23.720 --> 37:25.460
you must make sure you stay safe.

37:25.460 --> 37:28.690
♪ Night is painted with neon lights ♪

37:26.680 --> 37:28.030
Can you promise me that?

37:28.720 --> 37:29.430
Mu,

37:29.200 --> 37:32.280
♪ The softly bustling street ♪

37:29.910 --> 37:30.880
I'm so sorry.

37:31.470 --> 37:33.030
I didn't keep my promise to you.

37:32.500 --> 37:36.350
♪ I paused and wandered far ♪

37:34.160 --> 37:35.890
Today, when I tried to draw you,

37:36.280 --> 37:37.680
I realized the most painful thing

37:36.740 --> 37:40.390
♪ You're like a breeze ♪

37:38.070 --> 37:39.750
isn't that I can't hold the brush,

37:39.750 --> 37:41.540
but that even though
you're clearly in my memory,

37:41.180 --> 37:43.690
♪ I watch you leave ♪

37:41.880 --> 37:43.940
I can't even draw your hair properly.

37:44.470 --> 37:45.590
Lately, I often wonder,

37:44.500 --> 37:47.940
♪ I wish I could hug you from the back ♪

37:46.160 --> 37:47.560
if I hadn't gone that day,

37:48.070 --> 37:49.550
would everything have been different?

37:48.400 --> 37:51.470
♪ Lingering in the air ♪

37:50.640 --> 37:51.390
Sadly,

37:51.790 --> 37:54.940
♪ Your breath is everywhere ♪

37:52.200 --> 37:53.460
there are no what-ifs.

37:54.030 --> 37:54.760
Mu,

37:55.760 --> 37:57.820
You should go explore a bigger world.

37:58.640 --> 37:59.720
I will always wish you well.
